com.cube.storm.ui.lib.resolver

Class IntentResolverMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cube.storm.ui.lib.resolver.IntentResolverMap

  • public class IntentResolverMap
extends Object
    Intent resolver class used before IntentFactory to resolve any page using its ID/URI/Descriptor.

    This class should not be overridden, and accessed via UiSettings.getIntentResolver().
